app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: The following are available online, Figure S1: Mass spectra of crude methanol extract of different parts of Aniba tree from FLONA and RESEX. The peaks of anibine, reticuline, and 6-styryl-2-pyrone are highlighted. Figure S2: 1H-NMR spectra data from crude methanolic extract of FLONA, RESEX, A. parviflora, and A. rosiodora leaves. Figure S3: Loading plot from the PCA analysis using 1H NMR spectra data from crude methanolic extract of FLONA, RESEX, A. parviflora and A. rosiodora leaves.
